parameters:
Villain: Even among those aiming to be the strongest in the
dark organization, not a single one thought of defeating the
mayor... the cause of Dorietoku City's descent into the dark
ages. Thanks to Duke Shark, Dorietoku City has changed
drastically... He's on a whole different scale from us...

Memimi: Even I never thought of doing something about the
mayor at first... But somehow, I ended up doing something
big. In any case, maybe I was challenging him because I was
thinking of the city's future...

Villain: That former mayor, making Duke Shark appear in
adult videos and treating citizens like slaves... It was
crazy, but he forgave him and made him an ally... That's
something else... I had a grudge against him too, but after
watching that AV, I didn't care anymore, and now we're
getting along well.

Memimi: Ugh... I was worried whether the former corrupt
mayor, Orca Asparagus, would be able to fit in with the
citizens, but since he put me in an adult video, he's
surprisingly well-regarded... I feel like I'm the only one
who's really lost out here...

Thug: It's only been a little over half a year since Lord
Shark made his monster debut... In the blink of an eye, he
climbed to the top and even changed the future of the city.
Shark Broccoli was an amazing monster too, but you're even
beyond that...

Memimi: It's only because Lord Shark Broccoli picked me up
when I was collapsed on the road that I am who I am today.
I've continued to work hard because I wanted to be like that
great person...

Thug: (Even though she's the boss of a dark organization,
she's really a good kid...)

Thug: I know it's late, but I'm sorry for the gang rape the
other day... We all became subordinates in the same
organization, and you forgave us without any punishment...
You're a great boss...

Memimi: Enough, don't speak of that matter again... As the
supreme leader, I had no choice but to forgive... After all,
over 90% of the entire dark organization participated in
that incident... It's not like I can punish everyone one by
one...

Minion: Oh, great boss...! Thank you for your hard work, you
look beautiful today as well!! Ah, I'm so happy to be part
of such a wonderful boss's organization!!

Memimi: You don't need to flatter me that much... All the
organizations have been unified, and I've become the boss,
but I only directly intervene in illegal dealings, which
isn't much different from before.

Minion: Even so, thanks to your efforts in organizing and
mediating the dealings, and resolving the complications
between former organizations, our lives have become
incredibly easier! There are no more conflicts, and the town
has become a much more pleasant place to live!!

Memimi: Hmm hmm, never mind about me, from now on we must
all work together as one organization... I will do my best
so that everyone can live proudly in the light of day.

Minion: Even though you, our great boss, appeared in an
adult video and became someone who should be the least
visible in public, you're living normally, which gives us
dropouts hope. It shows that it's never too late, no matter
the situation...!

Memimi: ...I've told you to stop worrying about me... It's
not like I care about appearing in a little adult video...
It's just that my real name and school name got out and
spread on the internet, becoming a trend... ugh...

Tourist: Lord Shark is the most important person in Mudgain
City, right!? I read on the internet that he defeated the
mayor and became the Don of the underworld!

Memimi: That seems like a slightly misleading way to put
it... While he is the head of a dark organization, it's not
like he's the most important person in the city...

Tourist: Despite being such a small girl, she's a
respectable student council president, has the face of an
idol, and is incredibly strong in fights. She's even the
leader of a dark organization... It's a bit too much to take
in.

Memimi: Hehehe, tremble in fear... I am the perfect and
complete super monster! The underground city may be dark and
full of people from the dark organization, but the public
order is good, so feel free to enjoy yourself.

Tourist: The lip service is perfect too... As expected of
the great Shark Duke...! What a character...

Tourist: And to think she even appears in adult videos, it's
really anything goes. The streaming site might have shut
down, but her videos are still being shared all over the
internet, further deepening her popularity...

Memimi: In the end, I couldn't completely erase all the
videos and images, but there were some positive aspects to
it... surely... that's what I have to believe to be
satisfied... As a great leader, I must remain dignified no
matter what...

Tourist: Look, isn't that Lord Shark Duke?! Wow, so cool, so
cute~!

Tourist: I'm a Drillmaid fan, but it's lucky to see Lord
Shark Duke in person. I wonder if he'd give me an autograph
if I asked...

Memimi: Our battles as monsters of the dark organization
have become famous on the net, and Monster Fight is now a
hugely popular content streamed live worldwide. Thanks to
that, many fans visit the underground city where they can
meet their favorite monsters in person and spend lots of
money...
